# Reverse Engineering Antigravity Chat API — Full Walkthrough

## Tujuan
Mendapatkan akses ke **chat history** dan **real-time streaming** Antigravity IDE tanpa mengubah UI, untuk digunakan oleh Amaya Remote sebagai remote display.

---

## Fase 1: Analisis File [.pb](file:///C:/Users/BiuBiu/.gemini/antigravity/user_settings.pb) (❌ Gagal)

### Apa yang dilakukan
Antigravity menyimpan conversation di `~/.gemini/antigravity/conversations/*.pb`. Kami mencoba mendecodenya secara langsung.

### Hasil
- **Entropy: 7.96/8.0** → data terenkripsi, bukan sekadar compressed
- Semua metode dekompresi (gzip, zlib, bz2, lzma) gagal
- Tidak ada magic bytes yang dikenali
- **Kesimpulan: File [.pb](file:///C:/Users/BiuBiu/.gemini/antigravity/user_settings.pb) dienkripsi oleh Antigravity sebelum ditulis ke disk**

### Script yang digunakan
```python
# c:\tmp\analyze-pb.py — Entropy & compression analysis
```

---

## Fase 2: Reverse Engineering JavaScript (🔍 Research)

### Apa yang dilakukan
Membuka bundled JavaScript di:
```
%LOCALAPPDATA%\Programs\Antigravity\resources\app\extensions\antigravity\
├── dist\extension.js      ← Backend logic (Node.js)
├── out\media\chat.js      ← Chat UI (React webview)
└── bin\language_server_windows_x64.exe  ← gRPC Server binary
```

### Temuan Kunci
1. **`AgentClient`** di [chat.js](file:///C:/Users/BiuBiu/AppData/Local/Programs/Antigravity/resources/app/extensions/antigravity/out/media/chat.js) memanggil: [startConversation()](file:///c:/Users/BiuBiu/Documents/my%20app/amaya/amaya-remote-extension/src/extension.ts#595-640), [getConversation()](file:///c:/Users/BiuBiu/Documents/my%20app/amaya/app/src/main/java/com/amaya/intelligence/service/RemoteSessionClient.kt#118-121), [sendMessage()](file:///c:/Users/BiuBiu/Documents/my%20app/amaya/app/src/main/java/com/amaya/intelligence/ui/chat/ChatViewModel.kt#151-425), [deleteConversation()](file:///c:/Users/BiuBiu/Documents/my%20app/amaya/app/src/main/java/com/amaya/intelligence/ui/chat/ChatViewModel.kt#718-731), `reference()`, [stop()](file:///c:/Users/BiuBiu/Documents/my%20app/amaya/amaya-remote-extension/src/extension.ts#203-214)
2. Semua komunikasi melalui **Language Server** (binary Go/gRPC di `bin/`)
3. Schema protobuf menggunakan `exa.language_server_pb.LanguageServerService`

---

## Fase 3: Penemuan Port 53125 (🎯 Breakthrough!)

### Bagaimana ditemukan
User membuka **Chrome DevTools** (bawaan Antigravity/Electron) → Network tab → mengirim chat "hi" → muncul request ke:

```
https://127.0.0.1:53125/exa.language_server_pb.LanguageServerService/StartCascade
```

### Data yang dicapture dari DevTools

**Request Headers:**
```http
POST /exa.language_server_pb.LanguageServerService/StartCascade HTTP/2
Host: 127.0.0.1:53125
Content-Type: application/json
connect-protocol-version: 1
x-codeium-csrf-token: ec778089-b592-47d6-a07b-e08eca4eac0e
Origin: vscode-file://vscode-app
```

**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "metadata": {
    "ideName": "antigravity",
    "apiKey": "ya29.a0ATkoC...",   // Google OAuth token (expires ~1 hour)
    "locale": "en",
    "ideVersion": "1.19.6",
    "extensionName": "antigravity"
  },
  "source": "CORTEX_TRAJECTORY_SOURCE_CASCADE_CLIENT"
}
```

**Response Body:**
```json
{ "cascadeId": "411f11e9-10ed-4343-8369-49601470d7bb" }
```

