## Authentication

### Token 1: `x-codeium-csrf-token` (HTTP Header)
- UUID yang di-generate saat Antigravity start
- Berlaku selama sesi IDE
- Mencegah request dari luar browser process

### Token 2: `apiKey` dalam body (Google OAuth)
- Format: `ya29.a0ATkoC...` (Google OAuth 2.0 Access Token)
- Expires setiap ~1 jam
- Di-refresh otomatis oleh Antigravity
- Dikirim di dalam JSON body `metadata.apiKey`

---

## JSON Schema: Chat History

```json
{
  "trajectory": {
    "trajectoryId": "uuid",
    "cascadeId": "uuid",
    "trajectoryType": "CORTEX_TRAJECTORY_TYPE_CASCADE",
    "steps": [
      {
        "type": "CORTEX_STEP_TYPE_USER_INPUT",
        "status": "CORTEX_STEP_STATUS_DONE",
        "metadata": {
          "createdAt": "2026-03-07T21:27:38Z",
          "source": "CORTEX_STEP_SOURCE_USER_EXPLICIT"
        },
        "userInput": {
          "items": [{ "text": "hi" }],
          "activeUserState": { /* open files, cursor pos */ },
          "clientType": "CLIENT_TYPE_CHAT_PANEL"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "CORTEX_STEP_TYPE_PLANNER_RESPONSE",
        "plannerResponse": {
          "response": "Hello! How can I help you today?...",
          "thinking": "...",
          "thinkingDuration": "0.377725400s",
          "stopReason": "STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN"
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

### Step Types
| Type | Data Key | Isi |
|------|----------|-----|
| `USER_INPUT` | `userInput.items[0].text` | Pesan user |
| `PLANNER_RESPONSE` | `plannerResponse.response` | Jawaban AI |
| `CONVERSATION_HISTORY` | `conversationHistory` | History sebelumnya |
| `KNOWLEDGE_ARTIFACTS` | `knowledgeArtifacts` | Artifact yang di-load |
| `EPHEMERAL_MESSAGE` | `ephemeralMessage` | System message |
| `CHECKPOINT` | `checkpoint` | Checkpoint state |

