| Kebutuhan | Endpoint | Status |
|-----------|----------|--------|
| Baca history chat | `GetCascadeTrajectory` | ✅ Verified |
| List semua conversations | Scan `*.pb` + `GetCascadeTrajectory` | ✅ Verified |
| Kirim pesan baru | `SendUserCascadeMessage` | 🔄 Belum dites |
| Streaming real-time | `StreamCascadeReactiveUpdates` | 🔄 Belum dites |
